<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0">
<title>Barú Flood Index · River Soul</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@400;700&family=DM+Mono:wght@300;400;500&family=Lora:ital,wght@0,400;1,400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@supabase/supabase-js@2.49.1/dist/umd/supabase.min.js"></script>
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/chart.js@4.4.0/dist/chart.umd.min.js"></script>
<style>
  :root {
    --cream: #f7f2e8;
    --cream2: #ede6d6;
    --green-dark: #1a3a2a;
    --green: #2d6a4f;
    --green-light: #52b788;
    --teal: #0d7f7f;
    --teal-light: #48cae4;
    --amber: #e9a825;
    --red: #c0392b;
    --sand: #d4a96a;
    --ink: #1a2a20;
    --muted: #5a7a6a;
    --card: rgba(255,255,255,0.72);
    --card-border: rgba(45,106,79,0.15);
    --shadow: 0 2px 20px rgba(26,58,42,0.10);
  }
  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  body {
    background: var(--cream);
    color: var(--ink);
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    min-height: 100vh;
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }
  body::before {
    content: '';
    position: fixed; inset: 0;
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse at 15% 20%, rgba(82,183,136,0.10) 0%, transparent 55%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse at 85% 75%, rgba(72,202,228,0.08) 0%, transparent 50%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 50%, rgba(233,168,37,0.04) 0%, transparent 70%);
    pointer-events: none; z-index: 0;
  }

  .app { position: relative; z-index: 1; max-width: 480px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 0 80px; }

  /* ── Header ── */
  .header {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 28px 20px 16px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--card-border);
  }
  .header-eyebrow {
    font-size: 9px; letter-spacing: 0.22em; color: var(--muted);
    text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 6px;
  }
  .header h1 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 26px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--green-dark);
    line-height: 1.1;
  }
  .header-sub {
    font-size: 10px; color: var(--muted); margin-top: 4px; letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  }
  .season-badge {
    display: inline-block; margin-top: 10px;
    padding: 4px 14px; border-radius: 20px;
    font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    background: rgba(45,106,79,0.10);
    color: var(--green); border: 1px solid rgba(45,106,79,0.20);
  }

  /* ── Score ── */
  .score-ring {
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center;
    padding: 24px 20px 16px;
  }
  .ring-wrap {
    position: relative; width: 140px; height: 140px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .ring-wrap svg { transform: rotate(-90deg); }
  .ring-center {
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    display: flex; flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  }
  .ring-pct {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 30px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 1;
  }
  .ring-label {
    font-size: 9px; letter-spacing: 0.18em; margin-top: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .risk-chips {
    display: flex; gap: 8px; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center;
    font-size: 9px; letter-spacing: 0.12em;
  }
  .chip {
    padding: 3px 10px; border-radius: 10px;
    border: 1px solid currentColor; opacity: 0.75;
  }

  /* ── Tabs ── */
  .tabs {
    display: flex; overflow-x: auto;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--card-border);
    padding: 0 12px;
    scrollbar-width: none;
    -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;
  }
  .tabs::-webkit-scrollbar { display: none; }
  .tab-btn {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    background: none; border: none; cursor: pointer;
    padding: 10px 14px;
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 9px; letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--muted);
    border-bottom: 2px solid transparent;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }
  .tab-btn.active { color: var(--green); border-bottom-color: var(--green); }

  /* ── Content ── */
  .tab-content { display: none; padding: 16px; }
  .tab-content.active { display: block; }

  /* ── Cards ── */
  .card {
    background: var(--card);
    border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
    border-radius: 14px;
    padding: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
  }
  .card-title {
    font-size: 9px; letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 12px;
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px;
  }
  .card-title::after {
    content: ''; flex: 1; height: 1px; background: var(--card-border);
  }

  /* ── Factor bars ── */
  .factor-row { margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .factor-meta {
    display: flex; justify-content: space-between;
    font-size: 9px; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 4px;
  }
  .factor-track {
    height: 6px; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.06); border-radius: 3px; overflow: hidden;
  }
  .factor-fill {
    height: 100%; border-radius: 3px;
    transition: width 1s cubic-bezier(0.34, 1.56, 0.64, 1);
  }

  /* ── Grid stats ── */
  .stat-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 10px; }
  .stat-box {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
    border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
    border-radius: 10px; padding: 12px;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .stat-val {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 22px; color: var(--green-dark);
  }
  .stat-unit { font-size: 10px; color: var(--muted); }
  .stat-lbl { font-size: 9px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: var(--muted); margin-top: 3px; }

  /* ── Watershed comparison ── */
  .ws-row {
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 8px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
    font-size: 10px;
  }
  .ws-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .ws-name { color: var(--ink); font-size: 10px; }
  .ws-val { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 16px; color: var(--green-dark); }
  .ws-bar-wrap { flex: 1; margin: 0 10px; height: 4px; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.07); border-radius: 2px; }
  .ws-bar { height: 100%; border-radius: 2px; background: var(--teal-light); }
  .ws-avg-line {
    font-size: 9px; color: var(--muted); letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    padding: 8px 0 2px;
  }

  /* ── History chart ── */
  .chart-wrap { position: relative; height: 180px; margin-top: 8px; }

  /* ── Observation form ── */
  .obs-form label {
    display: block; font-size: 9px; letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 4px;
  }
  .obs-form input, .obs-form select, .obs-form textarea {
    width: 100%; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
    border: 1px solid var(--card-border); border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 9px 12px; font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px; color: var(--ink); margin-bottom: 10px;
    outline: none;
  }
  .obs-form textarea { resize: vertical; min-height: 60px; }
  .obs-form input:focus, .obs-form select:focus, .obs-form textarea:focus {
    border-color: var(--green-light);
  }
  .btn-submit {
    width: 100%; padding: 12px;
    background: var(--green); color: #fff;
    border: none; border-radius: 10px; cursor: pointer;
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase; transition: background 0.2s;
  }
  .btn-submit:hover { background: var(--green-dark); }
  .btn-submit:disabled { background: var(--muted); cursor: default; }

  /* ── History log ── */
  .log-row {
    display: flex; gap: 10px; align-items: flex-start;
    padding: 8px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
    font-size: 9px;
  }
  .log-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .log-time { color: var(--muted); flex-shrink: 0; width: 72px; }
  .log-score {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 14px; flex-shrink: 0; width: 32px;
  }
  .log-note { color: var(--ink); flex: 1; line-height: 1.5; }
  .log-tag {
    flex-shrink: 0; padding: 2px 7px; border-radius: 8px;
    font-size: 8px; letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    background: rgba(45,106,79,0.10); color: var(--green);
  }
  .log-tag.manual { background: rgba(233,168,37,0.12); color: #a07010; }

  /* ── Setup banner ── */
  .setup-banner {
    background: rgba(233,168,37,0.10);
    border: 1px solid rgba(233,168,37,0.30);
    border-radius: 10px; padding: 12px 14px;
    font-size: 10px; color: #7a5a10; margin-bottom: 14px;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
  .setup-banner strong { color: #5a3a00; }
  .setup-banner code {
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.08); padding: 1px 5px;
    border-radius: 4px; font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 9px;
  }

  /* ── IMN status ── */
  .imn-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr; gap: 8px; }
  .imn-cell {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
    border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
    border-radius: 8px; padding: 8px; text-align: center;
  }
  .imn-val { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 16px; color: var(--green-dark); }
  .imn-lbl { font-size: 8px; letter-spacing: 0.08em; color: var(--muted); }

  /* ── Forecast strip ── */
  .forecast-strip { display: flex; gap: 8px; overflow-x: auto; padding-bottom: 4px; scrollbar-width: none; }
  .forecast-strip::-webkit-scrollbar { display: none; }
  .fc-day {
    flex-shrink: 0; width: 68px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
    border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
    border-radius: 10px; padding: 10px 6px;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .fc-day-name { font-size: 8px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: var(--muted); text-transform: uppercase; }
  .fc-score {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 20px; margin: 4px 0 2px;
  }
  .fc-rain { font-size: 9px; color: var(--teal); }

  /* ── Loading ── */
  .loading-overlay {
    text-align: center; padding: 40px 20px;
    font-size: 10px; color: var(--muted); letter-spacing: 0.12em;
  }
  .loader {
    width: 32px; height: 32px; border-radius: 50%;
    border: 3px solid var(--cream2);
    border-top-color: var(--green);
    animation: spin 0.8s linear infinite;
    margin: 0 auto 12px;
  }
  @keyframes spin { to { transform: rotate(360deg); } }

  /* ── Error ── */
  .err { font-size: 9px; color: var(--red); padding: 6px 0; }

  /* ── Config panel ── */
  .config-section { margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .config-label {
    font-size: 9px; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 4px; display: block;
  }
  .config-input {
    width: 100%; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
    border: 1px solid var(--card-border); border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 8px 12px; font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10px; color: var(--ink); outline: none;
  }
  .btn-save {
    background: var(--teal); color: #fff;
    border: none; border-radius: 8px; padding: 8px 18px;
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 9px; letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase; cursor: pointer;
    margin-top: 6px;
  }

  .divider { height: 1px; background: var(--card-border); margin: 12px 0; }
  /* ── Flood Record ── */
  .flood-event {
    display: flex; gap: 14px; align-items: center;
    padding: 11px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(192,57,43,0.10);
  }
  .flood-event:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .flood-indicator {
    flex-shrink: 0; width: 28px; text-align: center;
  }
  .flood-dot {
    width: 10px; height: 10px; border-radius: 50%;
    background: #c0392b; margin: 0 auto;
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(192,57,43,0.12);
  }
  .flood-date {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 14px; color: #c0392b; flex-shrink: 0; width: 72px;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }
  .flood-date-sub { font-size: 8px; color: var(--muted); letter-spacing: 0.06em; }
  .flood-note { font-size: 9.5px; color: var(--ink); line-height: 1.6; font-family: 'Lora', serif; font-style: italic; flex: 1; }
  .flood-badge {
    flex-shrink: 0; font-size: 7.5px; letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 8px;
    background: rgba(192,57,43,0.10); color: #c0392b; text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  /* ── Journal ── */
  .journal-entry {
    padding: 14px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--card-border);
    display: flex;
    gap: 14px;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }
  .journal-entry:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .journal-date {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 36px;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .journal-day-num {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 26px;
    color: var(--green-dark);
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .journal-day-name {
    font-size: 7px;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    color: var(--muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-top: 2px;
  }
  .journal-body { flex: 1; }
  .journal-icons {
    font-size: 13px;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }
  .journal-text {
    font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--ink);
    line-height: 1.7;
    font-family: 'Lora', serif;
    font-style: italic;
  }
  .journal-tags {
    display: flex;
    gap: 5px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-top: 6px;
  }
  .journal-tag {
    font-size: 7.5px;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    padding: 2px 7px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    background: rgba(45,106,79,0.08);
    color: var(--green);
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .journal-tag.rain  { background: rgba(13,127,127,0.10); color: var(--teal); }
  .journal-tag.wind  { background: rgba(212,169,106,0.15); color: #8a6020; }
  .journal-tag.sun   { background: rgba(233,168,37,0.12); color: #8a6010; }
  .journal-tag.night { background: rgba(60,40,100,0.10); color: #5a3a80; }

  .footer {
    .footer {
    text-align: center; font-size: 8px; color: var(--muted);
    letter-spacing: 0.08em; padding: 8px 20px 0;
    line-height: 2;
  }
  .dot { display: inline-block; width: 5px; height: 5px; border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--green-light); margin-right: 5px; vertical-align: middle;
    animation: pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite; }
  @keyframes pulse { 0%,100%{opacity:1} 50%{opacity:0.3} }
  .live-badge { font-size: 8px; color: var(--green); letter-spacing: 0.1em; }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="app">

  <!-- Header -->
  <div class="header">
    <div class="header-eyebrow">River Soul · Dominical, CR</div>
    <h1>Barú Flood Index</h1>
    <div class="header-sub" id="header-time">Loading…</div>
    <div class="season-badge" id="season-badge">Dry Season · March</div>
  </div>

  <!-- Score Ring -->
  <div class="score-ring">
    <div class="ring-wrap">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 140 140" width="140" height="140">
        <circle cx="70" cy="70" r="58" fill="none" stroke="rgba(0,0,0,0.07)" stroke-width="10"/>
        <circle id="ring-arc" cx="70" cy="70" r="58" fill="none"
          stroke="#1e8449" stroke-width="10" stroke-linecap="round"
          stroke-dasharray="364.4" stroke-dashoffset="364.4"/>
      </svg>
      <div class="ring-center">
        <div class="ring-pct" id="ring-pct" style="color:#1e8449">—</div>
        <div class="ring-label" id="ring-label" style="color:#1e8449">LOADING</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="risk-chips" id="risk-chips">
      <span class="chip" style="color:#888">Fetching data…</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Tabs -->
  <div class="tabs">
    <button class="tab-btn active" onclick="switchTab('overview')">Overview</button>
    <button class="tab-btn" onclick="switchTab('watershed')">Watershed</button>
    <button class="tab-btn" onclick="switchTab('stations')">Stations</button>
    <button class="tab-btn" onclick="switchTab('forecast')">Forecast</button>
    <button class="tab-btn" onclick="switchTab('historical')">Historical</button>
    <button class="tab-btn" onclick="switchTab('history')">History</button>
    <button class="tab-btn" onclick="switchTab('observe')">Log</button>
    <button class="tab-btn" onclick="switchTab('journal')">Journal</button>
    <button class="tab-btn" onclick="switchTab('config')">Config</button>
  </div>

  <!-- ═══════════════ OVERVIEW ═══════════════ -->
  <div id="tab-overview" class="tab-content active">
    <div id="overview-loading" class="loading-overlay">
      <div class="loader"></div>
      Fetching live conditions…
    </div>
    <div id="overview-content" style="display:none">

      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-title">Current Conditions</div>
        <div class="stat-grid">
          <div class="stat-box">
            <div class="stat-val" id="ov-rain24">—</div>
            <div class="stat-unit">mm</div>
            <div class="stat-lbl">Rain 24h</div>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-box">
            <div class="stat-val" id="ov-rain72">—</div>
            <div class="stat-unit">mm</div>
            <div class="stat-lbl">Rain 72h</div>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-box">
            <div class="stat-val" id="ov-temp">—</div>
            <div class="stat-unit">°C</div>
            <div class="stat-lbl">Temperature</div>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-box">
            <div class="stat-val" id="ov-humid">—</div>
            <div class="stat-unit">%</div>
            <div class="stat-lbl">Humidity</div>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-box">
            <div class="stat-val" id="ov-wind">—</div>
            <div class="stat-unit">km/h</div>
            <div class="stat-lbl">Wind</div>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-box">
            <div class="stat-val" id="ov-soil">—</div>
            <div class="stat-unit">m³/m³</div>
            <div class="stat-lbl">Soil Moisture</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-title">Flood Risk Factors</div>
        <div id="factor-bars"></div>
        <div style="font-size:9px;color:var(--muted);margin-top:10px;line-height:1.8;font-family:'DM Mono',monospace" id="score-formula"></div>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-title">Tide · Bahía Uvita</div>
        <div class="stat-grid" style="grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr 1fr">
          <div class="stat-box">
            <div class="stat-val" id="ov-tide">—</div>
            <div class="stat-unit">m</div>
            <div class="stat-lbl">Now</div>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-box">
            <div class="stat-val" id="ov-tide-next-val">—</div>
            <div class="stat-unit" id="ov-tide-next-type">—</div>
            <div class="stat-lbl" id="ov-tide-next-time">next</div>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-box">
            <canvas id="moon-canvas" width="64" height="64" style="display:block;margin:0 auto 4px"></canvas>
            <div style="font-size:8px;color:var(--ink);letter-spacing:0.04em;line-height:1.3" id="ov-lunar-name">—</div>
            <div style="font-size:7px;color:var(--muted)" id="ov-lunar-pct"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div style="margin-top:12px">
          <div style="font-size:8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:6px">24H TIDE CHART</div>
          <div style="position:relative;height:80px"><canvas id="tide-chart"></canvas></div>
        </div>
        <div style="font-size:8px;color:var(--muted);margin-top:8px;text-align:center;letter-spacing:0.06em">
          Harmonic model · M2 S2 N2 K1 O1 · calibrated Pacífico Sur
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ═══════════════ WATERSHED ═══════════════ -->
  <div id="tab-watershed" class="tab-content">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-title">Watershed Rainfall — 3 Stations Averaged</div>
      <div id="ws-loading" class="loading-overlay" style="padding:20px">
        <div class="loader"></div>Fetching upstream data…
      </div>
      <div id="ws-content" style="display:none">
        <div style="font-size:9px;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:10px;line-height:1.7">
          Averaging rainfall across the Barú watershed: river mouth crossing, Platanillo mid-valley (408m), and Tinamastes upper catchment (754m). All three are in Barú district and drain directly into the river.
          A high upstream average predicts a surge <span style="color:var(--green)">2–6 hours</span> before it arrives at the crossing.
        </div>
        <div id="ws-rows"></div>
        <div class="divider"></div>
